<collectionCode id="ED34AE6EEE0EFFCEFBAFFAF4FB2F500E" box="[1096,1157,1337,1361]" country="Iran" httpUri="http://biocol.org/urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:13098" lsid="urn:lsid:biocol.org:col:13098" name="Tehran University" pageId="7" pageNumber="146" type="Herbarium">TUH</collectionCode>
)
</materialsCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="C33F6520EE0EFFCEFCCAFAB9FBED52B3" pageId="7" pageNumber="146" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B9A36ABEE0EFFCEFCCAFAB9FC2250D3" blockId="7.[813,1457,1396,1805]" box="[813,904,1396,1422]" pageId="7" pageNumber="146">REMARK</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B9A36ABEE0EFFCEFCCAFA59FC755252" blockId="7.[813,1457,1396,1805]" pageId="7" pageNumber="146">
<taxonomicName id="4C254D28EE0EFFCEFCCAFA59FC3B50F2" box="[813,913,1428,1454]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Cotoneaster" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="7" pageNumber="146" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="meyeri">
<emphasis id="B951EAB9EE0EFFCEFCCAFA59FC3B50F2" box="[813,913,1428,1454]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="146">C. meyeri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is reported from north 
<collectingCountry id="F332763BEE0EFFCEFB73FA59FB6850F1" box="[1172,1218,1428,1454]" name="Iran" pageId="7" pageNumber="146">Iran</collectingCountry>
in 
<collectingRegion id="49E1F849EE0EFFCEFB03FA5EFCF15092" country="Iran" name="Mazandaran" pageId="7" pageNumber="146">Mazandaran province</collectingRegion>
(
<figureCitation id="131E2A2EEE0EFFCEFC8AFA7EFC6C5091" box="[877,966,1459,1486]" captionStart="FIG" captionStartId="11.[132,143,1986,2003]" captionTargetBox="[231,1361,215,1802]" captionTargetId="figure-19@11.[231,1361,215,1803]" captionTargetPageId="11" captionText="FIG. 7. — Cotoneaster meyeri Pojark. leaves and fruits outline (A) and close up (B). Collection number: Raei Niaki &amp; Mahdigholi 46883 (TUH); determined by Raei Niaki &amp; Attar." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6573127" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6573127/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="146">Fig. 7A</figureCitation>
). The species belongs to subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="4C254D28EE0EFFCEFAB1FA7EFC2E50B2" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Chaenopetalum" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="7" pageNumber="146" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="B951EAB9EE0EFFCEFAB1FA7EFC2E50B2" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="146">Chaenopetalum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFB44B5AEE0EFFCEFC72FA19FB2250B2" author="FRYER J. &amp; HYLMO B." box="[917,1160,1491,1518]" pageId="7" pageNumber="146" refId="ref4629" refString="FRYER J. &amp; HYLMO B. 2009. - Cotoneasters: A Comprehensive Guide to Shrubs for Flowers, Fruit, and Foliage. Timber press, Portland, London, 344 p." type="book" year="2009">Fryer &amp; Hylmö 2009</bibRefCitation>
). This species is related to 
<taxonomicName id="4C254D28EE0EFFCEFCCAFA39FBBC5351" authority="Bunge" authorityName="Bunge" box="[813,1046,1523,1550]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Cotoneaster" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="7" pageNumber="146" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="multiflorus">
<emphasis id="B951EAB9EE0EFFCEFCCAFA39FC6C5352" box="[813,966,1523,1550]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="146">C. multiflorus</emphasis>
Bunge
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFB44B5AEE0EFFCEFBCEFA3EFB6C5352" author="BROWICZ K." box="[1065,1222,1523,1549]" pageId="7" pageNumber="146" pagination="32" refId="ref4539" refString="BROWICZ K. 1972. - Cotoneaster Medik., in DAVIS P. H. (ed.), Flora of Turkey. Edinburgh University Press, Edinburgh 4: L 2 g-L 32." type="journal article" year="1972">Browicz 1972</bibRefCitation>
), from which it differs for its black-purple fruits (vs light red to red), acute to obtuse (vs obtuse to rounded) and shorter leaves (
<quantity id="4CDD9B4EEE0EFFCEFA6CF9FEFCD45332" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.7" metricValueMax="3.9" metricValueMin="1.5" pageId="7" pageNumber="146" unit="mm" value="27.0" valueMax="39.0" valueMin="15.0">15- 39 mm</quantity>
vs 
<quantity id="4CDD9B4EEE0EFFCEFC44F99EFBB55332" box="[931,1055,1619,1646]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.75" metricValueMax="5.5" metricValueMin="2.0" pageId="7" pageNumber="146" unit="mm" value="37.5" valueMax="55.0" valueMin="20.0">20-55 mm</quantity>
), fewer- flowered inflorescence (5-8 vs 5-13) and indumentum of pedicel in fruit (glabrous vs thinly tomentose) (
<figureCitation id="131E2A2EEE0EFFCEFBE9F95EFBCD53F2" box="[1038,1127,1683,1709]" captionStart="FIG" captionStartId="11.[132,143,1986,2003]" captionTargetBox="[231,1361,215,1802]" captionTargetId="figure-19@11.[231,1361,215,1803]" captionTargetPageId="11" captionText="FIG. 7. — Cotoneaster meyeri Pojark. leaves and fruits outline (A) and close up (B). Collection number: Raei Niaki &amp; Mahdigholi 46883 (TUH); determined by Raei Niaki &amp; Attar." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6573127" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6573127/files/figure.png" pageId="7" pageNumber="146">Fig. 7B</figureCitation>
). The geographical distribution of the species is 
<collectingCountry id="F332763BEE0EFFCEFBFDF97FFB0E5393" box="[1050,1188,1714,1740]" name="Afghanistan" pageId="7" pageNumber="146">Afghanistan</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F332763BEE0EFFCEFB48F97FFA8A5393" box="[1199,1312,1714,1740]" name="Tajikistan" pageId="7" pageNumber="146">Tajikistan</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry id="F332763BEE0EFFCEFACBF97EFA005392" box="[1324,1450,1715,1741]" name="Kyrgyzstan" pageId="7" pageNumber="146">Kyrgyzstan</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingRegion id="49E1F849EE0EFFCEFCCAF91FFC0E53B3" box="[813,932,1746,1772]" country="Iran" name="Azarbayjan-e Sharqi" pageId="7" pageNumber="146">Azerbaijan</collectingRegion>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFB44B5AEE0EFFCEFC52F91FFB9853B3" author="RIEDL H." box="[949,1074,1746,1772]" pageId="7" pageNumber="146" pagination="13 - 26" refId="ref5495" refString="RIEDL H. 1969. - Cotoneaster Medik., in RECHINGER K. H. (ed.), Flora Iranica. Akademische Druck und Verlagsanstalt, Graz 66: 13 - 26." type="journal article" year="1969">Riedl 1969</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFB44B5AEE0EFFCEFBA6F91FFB5A53B2" author="POJARKOVA A. I." box="[1089,1264,1746,1773]" pageId="7" pageNumber="146" pagination="259 - 274" refId="ref5207" refString="POJARKOVA A. I. 1971. - Cotoneaster Medik., in KOMAROV V. L. (ed.), Flora of USSR. Keter press, Jerusalem 9: 259 - 274." type="journal article" year="1971">Pojarkova 1971</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EFB44B5AEE0EFFCEFB18F91EFCCD5253" author="FRYER J. &amp; HYLMO B." pageId="7" pageNumber="146" refId="ref4629" refString="FRYER J. &amp; HYLMO B. 2009. - Cotoneasters: A Comprehensive Guide to Shrubs for Flowers, Fruit, and Foliage. Timber press, Portland, London, 344 p." type="book" year="2009">Fryer &amp; Hylmö 2009</bibRefCitation>
) and 
<collectingCountry id="F332763BEE0EFFCEFC4EF93EFC715252" box="[937,987,1779,1805]" name="Iran" pageId="7" pageNumber="146">Iran</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B9A36ABEE0EFFCEFCCAF8FEFCC45214" blockId="7.[812,1456,1843,2028]" box="[813,878,1843,1869]" pageId="7" pageNumber="146">NOTE</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B9A36ABEE0EFFCEFCCAF89FFBED52B3" blockId="7.[812,1456,1843,2028]" pageId="7" pageNumber="146">
<taxonomicName id="4C254D28EE0EFFCEFCCAF89FFC3A5233" box="[813,912,1874,1900]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Rosaceae" genus="Cotoneaster" kingdom="Plantae" order="Rosales" pageId="7" pageNumber="146" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="meyeri">
<emphasis id="B951EAB9EE0EFFCEFCCAF89FFC3A5233" box="[813,912,1874,1900]" italics="true" pageId="7" pageNumber="146">C. meyeri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
was not previously reported from the flora of 
<collectingCountry id="F332763BEE0EFFCEFA64F89EFA1A5232" box="[1411,1456,1875,1901]" name="Iran" pageId="7" pageNumber="146">Iran</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EFB44B5AEE0EFFCEFCD1F8BFFC0552D3" author="RIEDL H." box="[822,943,1906,1932]" pageId="7" pageNumber="146" pagination="13 - 26" refId="ref5495" refString="RIEDL H. 1969. - Cotoneaster Medik., in RECHINGER K. H. (ed.), Flora Iranica. Akademische Druck und Verlagsanstalt, Graz 66: 13 - 26." type="journal article" year="1969">Riedl 1969</bibRefCitation>
). Later, this species was reported there without locality information (
<bibRefCitation id="EFB44B5AEE0EFFCEFBFFF85FFAAF52F3" author="FRYER J. &amp; HYLMO B." box="[1048,1285,1938,1964]" pageId="7" pageNumber="146" refId="ref4629" refString="FRYER J. &amp; HYLMO B. 2009. - Cotoneasters: A Comprehensive Guide to Shrubs for Flowers, Fruit, and Foliage. Timber press, Portland, London, 344 p." type="book" year="2009">Fryer &amp; Hylmö 2009</bibRefCitation>
). In the framework of this paper, this species was collected again, and it is reported for Flora of 
<collectingCountry id="F332763BEE0EFFCEFBF4F81FFBE952B3" box="[1043,1091,2002,2028]" name="Iran" pageId="7" pageNumber="146">Iran</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
